<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>Drive Access Auditor does not collect, store, or transmit personal data.</p>

<p>The add-on operates entirely within the user's Google account and uses read-only access to Google Drive metadata to display sharing information.</p>

<p>No file contents are accessed and no data is sent to external servers.</p>

<p>If you have questions, contact: atulbhandari@gmail.com</p>
